msgid ""
"Specifically: <span class=\"tw-font-bold\">37,380 volunteers</span> across <span class=\"tw-font-bold\">190 countries</span> installed Mozilla’s RegretsReporter browser extensions for Firefox and "
"Chrome."
msgstr ""
"Plus précisément : <span class=\"tw-font-bold\">37 380 bénévoles</span> originaires de <span class=\"tw-font-bold\">190 pays</span> ont installé l’extension RegretsReporter de Mozilla sur Firefox et"
" Chrome. "

